				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Enjoyed the obsessed lead character a lot in this.Love the internal justifications and misguided interpretation of evidence.<br />
I enjoyed that fact that he was an actor and famous thus the rationalisations seem more reasonable &#8211; &#8216;keeping up the hetro-facade&#8217; <img src="http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/wp-includes/images/smilies/simple-smile.png" alt=":)" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p>
<p>I think it might be better if it were a little less over the top but I felt a deep sad sympathy for the character &#8211; his near-insane world-view is kind of sweet and innocent. I like the way there is no sense of violence or anger in his obsession.</p>
